<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <title>New Reply to Your Question</title>
        <style>
            body {
                font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                font-size: 16px;
                line-height: 1.5;
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }
            ul {
                list-style: none;
                padding: 0;
                margin: 0;
            }
            li {
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }
            p {
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>New Reply to Your Question</h1>
        <p>Dear <%= name %>,</p>
        <p>We are writing to inform you that your question has received a new reply.</p>
        <p>The details of the reply are as follows:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Question: <%= title %></li>
        </ul>
        <p>Please log in to your account to view the reply and continue the discussion.</p>
        <p>Thank you for using our platform.</p>
        <p>Sincerely,</p>
        <p>The LMS Team</p>
    </body>
</html>
